Courtesy #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - Tired of waiting for help and after nearly two months of living in halls and shelters since the April floods, a group of KZN flood victims have occupied the eThekwini City Hall. Watch the video above for more details.   A large group of people is gathering at the City Hall. We believe they are flood victims, who’ve been reeling from last month's devasting floods. eNCA reporter Manqoba Mchunu is there. #DStv403